content.rendered:
Directed by Koratala Siva.

Written by Koratala Siva.

Cast Mohanlal(Sathyam). N.T. Rama Rao Jr.(Anand). Samantha Ruth Prabhu(Bujji). Nithya Menen(Anu (as Nithya Menon)). Kajal Aggarwal(Nenu Pakka Local). Unni Mukundan(Raghava). Ajay(Bose). Suresh(Suresh). Saikumar(Chandra Sekhar). Devayani(Prabha). Sai Kumar(Chandrashekhar IPS). Sachin Khedekar(Mukesh). Rahman(Shiva). Sithara(Bujji’s mother). Rajeev Kanakala(Vikas). Vijayakumar(Chief Minister (as Vijay Kumar)). Vennela Kishore(Pyarelal). Brahmaji(Shankar). Banerjee(Saidulu). John Kokken(Satpal).Aravind. Santosh Kumar Yadav(Hero Friend). Chalapathi Rao(DGP). Rajitha(Dinesh’s mother). Ram Charan Teja(Rajeev Kanakala’s Son (as Charan Ram)).Sravan. Jeeva(Bujji’s boss). Anitha Chowdary(Anu’s mother).Gayatri Bhargavi.Mahindra. Vidisha Srivastav(Riya).Prabhu.Feroz Abbasi.Venugopal.Shashidhar . Jagapathi Babu(Narrator (voice)). Sandeep Hemnaoni(Villains son (as Sundip Ved)). Ravi Prakash(Dinesh Kumar).Meena Vasu. Ashish Vidyarthi(Raghava’s bussines partner)

Language Telugu.

Producers Mohan Cherukuri. P.T. Giridhar Rao. Chandrashekhar Ravipati. Y. Ravi Shankar. Naveen Yerneni.

Production Mythri Movie Makers. Goldmines Telefilms.
